<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ระบบชำระค่าธรรมเนียมการศึกษา</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sarabun:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Noto+Serif+Thai:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        :root {
            --navy: #0a1f44;
            --navy-mid: #122a5e;
            --gold: #c9a84c;
            --gold-light: #e8c97a;
            --gold-pale: #f5e6bb;
            --cream: #fdf8ee;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --gray: #6b7280;
            --border: rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.3);
            --green: #16a34a;
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Sarabun', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--cream);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            background-image:
                radial-gradient(ellipse at top, rgba(18,42,94,0.06) 0%, transparent 60%),
                repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, transparent 40px, rgba(201,168,76,0.03) 40px, rgba(201,168,76,0.03) 41px);
        }

        /* HEADER */
        .header {
            width: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, var(--navy-mid) 100%);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(10,31,68,0.35);
        }
        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, transparent 60px, rgba(201,168,76,0.04) 60px, rgba(201,168,76,0.04) 61px);
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .header-gold-bar {
            height: 5px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold) 0%, var(--gold-light) 50%, var(--gold) 100%);
        }
        .header-inner {
            max-width: 960px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 28px 32px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 24px;
        }
        .emblem { width: 80px; height: 80px; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .emblem svg { width: 80px; height: 80px; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(201,168,76,0.4)); }
        .header-text { flex: 1; }
        .agency-name {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif Thai', serif;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--gold-light);
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: 0.03em;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }
        .system-title {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif Thai', serif;
            font-size: 1.55rem;
            color: var(--white);
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .header-divider {
            width: 2px; height: 60px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, var(--gold), transparent);
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .header-sub {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
            line-height: 1.9;
            text-align: right;
        }

        /* MAIN */
        main {
            flex: 1;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 960px;
            padding: 40px 24px 60px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 28px;
        }

        /* Breadcrumb */
        .breadcrumb {
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            color: var(--gray);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            animation: fadeSlideDown 0.5s ease both;
        }
        .breadcrumb span { color: var(--gold); }

        /* Steps bar */
        .steps-bar {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            animation: fadeSlideUp 0.5s ease both;
        }
        .step {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .step:not(:last-child)::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 18px;
            left: 55%;
            right: -55%;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--border);
            z-index: 0;
        }
        .step-circle {
            width: 36px; height: 36px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 2px solid var(--border);
            background: var(--white);
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--gray);
            z-index: 1;
            position: relative;
        }
        .step.active .step-circle {
            border-color: var(--gold);
            background: var(--gold);
            color: var(--navy);
        }
        .step-label {
            font-size: 0.72rem;
            color: var(--gray);
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .step.active .step-label { color: var(--navy); font-weight: 600; }

        /* Card */
        .card {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 580px;
            background: var(--white);
            border-radius: 4px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(10,31,68,0.06), 0 12px 40px rgba(10,31,68,0.08);
            overflow: hidden;
            animation: fadeSlideUp 0.6s ease both;
            animation-delay: 0.1s;
        }
        .card-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, var(--navy-mid) 100%);
            padding: 22px 32px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .card-header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), var(--gold-light), var(--gold));
        }
        .card-header-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; }
        .card-header-icon {
            width: 42px; height: 42px;
            background: rgba(201,168,76,0.15);
            border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
            border-radius: 2px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .card-header-icon svg { color: var(--gold-light); }
        .card-title {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif Thai', serif;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            color: var(--white);
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }
        .card-subtitle { font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45); }

        .card-body { padding: 32px 32px; }

        /* Form */
        .form-group { margin-bottom: 24px; }
        label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.84rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--navy);
            margin-bottom: 9px;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        }
        label .required { color: #c0392b; margin-left: 3px; }
        .input-wrapper { position: relative; }
        .input-icon {
            position: absolute;
            left: 14px; top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            color: #9ca3af;
            pointer-events: none;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }
        input[type="text"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 13px 16px 13px 44px;
            font-family: 'Sarabun', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            color: var(--navy);
            background: var(--cream);
            border: 1.5px solid #d1d5db;
            border-radius: 3px;
            outline: none;
            transition: all 0.25s ease;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }
        input[type="text"]::placeholder { color: #c4c9d4; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-weight: 300; }
        input[type="text"]:focus {
            border-color: var(--gold);
            background: var(--white);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(201,168,76,0.12);
        }
        .input-wrapper:focus-within .input-icon { color: var(--gold); }

        .hint {
            margin-top: 8px;
            font-size: 0.77rem;
            color: var(--gray);
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Button */
        .btn {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px 24px;
            font-family: 'Sarabun', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--navy);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold) 0%, var(--gold-light) 50%, var(--gold) 100%);
            background-size: 200% auto;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 3px;
            cursor: pointer;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(201,168,76,0.35);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .btn::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute; inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.2), transparent);
            opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s;
        }
        .btn:hover { background-position: right center; box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(201,168,76,0.5); transform: translateY(-1px); }
        .btn:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
        .btn:active { transform: translateY(0); box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(201,168,76,0.3); }

        /* Divider */
        .divider {
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
            margin: 26px 0 18px;
        }
        .divider-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--border), transparent); }
        .divider-text { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #9ca3af; letter-spacing: 0.06em; white-space: nowrap; }

        /* Info box */
        .info-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201,168,76,0.06), rgba(201,168,76,0.02));
            border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
            border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
            border-radius: 2px;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            font-size: 0.79rem;
            color: #6b5d3e;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .info-box strong { color: #8a6d2e; font-weight: 700; }

        /* Fee type tags */
        .fee-tags {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }
        .fee-tag {
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
            background: rgba(10,31,68,0.04);
            border: 1px solid rgba(10,31,68,0.1);
            border-radius: 2px;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--navy);
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .fee-tag-dot {
            width: 7px; height: 7px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--gold);
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        /* FOOTER */
        footer {
            width: 100%;
            background: var(--navy);
            padding: 18px 32px;
            border-top: 3px solid var(--gold);
        }
        .footer-inner {
            max-width: 960px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .footer-text { font-size: 0.75rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.38); line-height: 1.7; }
        .footer-badge {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: var(--gold);
            border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 2px;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        }

        @keyframes fadeSlideUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        @keyframes fadeSlideDown {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .header-inner { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
            .header-divider { width: 60px; height: 2px; }
            .system-title { font-size: 1.25rem; }
            .card-body { padding: 24px 20px; }
            .footer-inner { flex-direction: column; }
            .header-sub { text-align: center; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>



<main>

    

    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-header-row">
                <div class="card-header-icon">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="card-subtitle">กรอกรหัสประจำตัวนักเรียนเพื่อดูรายการค่าธรรมเนียมที่ต้องชำระ</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card-body">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="id">
                    รหัสประจำตัวนักเรียน
                    <span class="required">*</span>
                </label>
                <div class="input-wrapper">
                    <svg class="input-icon" width="18" height="18" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 6H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v9a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2h-5m-4 0V5a2 2 0 114 0v1m-4 0a2 2 0 104 0m-5 8a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4zm0 0c1.306 0 2.417.835 2.83 2M9 14a3.001 3.001 0 00-2.83 2"/>
                    </svg>
                    <input
                        type="text"
                        id="id"
                        placeholder="XXXX"
                        autocomplete="off"
                        maxlength="20"
                        onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter') goTomoney()"
                    >
                </div>
                <div class="hint">
                    <svg width="13" height="13" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
                    รหัสประจำตัวนักเรียนอยู่ในบัตรนักเรียน หรือเอกสารทะเบียนที่ได้รับจากสถานศึกษา
                </div>
            </div>

            <button class="btn" onclick="goTomoney()">
                <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/>
                </svg>
                ค้นหาข้อมูลและรายการค่าธรรมเนียม
            </button>

            <div class="divider">
                <div class="divider-line"></div>
                <div class="divider-text">ประเภทค่าธรรมเนียมที่ชำระได้ในระบบ</div>
                <div class="divider-line"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="fee-tags">
                <div class="fee-tag"><div class="fee-tag-dot"></div>ค่าธรรมเนียมการเรียน</div>
                <div class="fee-tag"><div class="fee-tag-dot"></div>ค่าบำรุงการศึกษา</div>
                <div class="fee-tag"><div class="fee-tag-dot"></div>ค่าอุปกรณ์การเรียน</div>
                <div class="fee-tag"><div class="fee-tag-dot"></div>ค่าเครื่องแบบนักเรียน</div>
                <div class="fee-tag"><div class="fee-tag-dot"></div>ค่ากิจกรรมพัฒนาผู้เรียน</div>
            </div>

           
        </div>
    </div>

</main>


<script>
    function goTomoney() {
        const idDom = document.querySelector("#id");
        const id = idDom.value.trim();

        if (!id) {
            idDom.focus();
            idDom.style.borderColor = '#c0392b';
            idDom.style.boxShadow = '0 0 0 3px rgba(192,57,43,0.12)';
            setTimeout(() => {
                idDom.style.borderColor = '';
                idDom.style.boxShadow = '';
            }, 2000);
            return;
        }

        window.open("/moneying/" + id, "_blank");
    }
</script>

</body>
</html>